description.en: FlokiPup Inu is fully decentralized and owned by a fun, vibrant community. They welcome and embrace diverse perspectives to build FlokiPup Inu into the best community in crypto. With every transaction in FlokiPup Inu's network (buy or sell), 5% of the transaction is distributed to existing holders. That means you earn $FLOKIPUP just by holding it in your wallet.
